name: Parasite Paranoid
desc: (Quick Effect): You can target 1 face-up monster on the field; equip this card from your hand to that target. You can only use this effect of "Parasite Paranoid" once per turn. The equipped monster becomes Insect, it cannot attack Insect monsters, also negate its activated effects that target Insect monsters. If this Equip Card is sent to the GY: You can Special Summon 1 Level 7 or higher Insect monster from your hand, ignoring its Summoning conditions.
